snippet.title: Jack N' Jill - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Jack N' Jill is a retro one button platformer for the iPhone / iPad, Android, the Mac and the Ouya. Help Jack find Jill by guiding him through 140 levels filled with obstacles of different types.

App Store: http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/jack-n...

Google Play: http://play.google.com/store/apps/det...

Mac App Store: http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/jack-n...

Windows Store: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/games/jack-n-jill/9nblggh5szbx

Soundtrack: http://rohannarang.bandcamp.com/releases
